name: AudioWorkletProcessor
description: The AudioWorkletProcessor interface of the Web Audio API represents an audio processing code behind a custom AudioWorkletNode. It lives in the AudioWorkletGlobalScope and runs on the Web Audio rendering thread. In turn, an AudioWorkletNode based on it runs on the main thread.
